  29:  * This allows creating a large number of PulsarClient instances in a single JVM without wasting resources.
  30:  * Sharing the DNS resolver and cache will help reduce the number of DNS lookups performed by the clients
  31:  * and improve latency and reduce load on the DNS servers.
